## LoggingWithAppenderExample.java

```java
import org.slf4j.Logger;
import org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;

public class LoggingWithAppenderExample {

    private static final Logger logger =
            LoggerFactory.getLogger(LoggingWithAppenderExample.class);

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        logger.trace("Trace Message");

        logger.debug("Debug Message");

        logger.info("Information Message");

        logger.warn("Warning Message");

        logger.error("Error Message");

    }
}
```

### Output

**Console**

```text
10:20:45 INFO  LoggingWithAppenderExample - Information Message
10:20:45 WARN  LoggingWithAppenderExample - Warning Message
10:20:45 ERROR LoggingWithAppenderExample - Error Message
```

**File (app.log)**

```text
10:20:45 INFO  LoggingWithAppenderExample - Information Message
10:20:45 WARN  LoggingWithAppenderExample - Warning Message
10:20:45 ERROR LoggingWithAppenderExample - Error Message
```

